node.text:
Carlos Sainz lost control of his Ferrari on the entry to Turn 3 before colliding with the barriers during final practice at Zandvoort.

#DutchGP 🇳🇱 #Formula1 #F1

First Zandvoort winner this weekend is Arthur Leclerc in @fiaf3! 🏆

And his brother @charles_leclerc was on hand to congratulate him on a second F3 win of the season!

#F3 #Formula3 #RoadToF1 #Motorsport #Racing
